                    <span>Buying this book new is a bit pricey. I bought a used copy and it was worth every penny. If you can't find it used, then spend the full price to buy it new. I can't imagine administering my FreeBSD server without this book. I had tried a couple other books that weren't nearly has useful as this one.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Great, but also get Essential System Administration</div>
